Package: RegCompassR
Title: Simplified Multiome-Supported Reaction Capacity Potential Analysis
Version: 0.9.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "RegCompass", family = "Developers", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "dev@example.com"))
Description: Provides a simplified Layer 1 workflow for annotated Seurat v4 RNA+ATAC multiome objects: raw RNA count extraction, sample-aware cell-type micropooling, pool-summed logCPM normalization, robust GPR-aware reaction capacity potential, cell-type Q95 calibration, reaction evidence scores with per-reaction RNA detection fallback and missing-GPR penalties, and minimal diagnostics.
